[I] File archiver

[T] Engrampa is an archive manager for the MATE environment. This means that
[T] you can create and modify archives; view the content of an archive; view
[T] and modify a file contained in the archive; extract files from the archive.

[U] https://mate-desktop.org/

[A] MATE developer
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/desktop/mate

[E] add fontconfig shared-mime-info

[L] GPL
[V] 1.28.3

